flowchart TD
    START([discover_session_files]) --> SCAN[Scan ~/.claude/projects/*//*.jsonl]
    SCAN --> LOOP{Next file?}

    LOOP -->|Yes| MTIME{Modified<br>> 30 min ago?}
    MTIME -->|No| LOOP
    MTIME -->|Yes| PREV[get_session_line_count<br>from state]

    PREV --> LEGACY{Legacy entry<br>line_count = -1?}
    LEGACY -->|Yes| LOOP
    LEGACY -->|No| PARSE[parse_session_file<br>skip_lines = prev_count]

    PARSE --> GREW{total_lines ><br>prev_count?}
    GREW -->|No| LOOP
    GREW -->|Yes| CONTENT{New prompts<br>or tools?}

    CONTENT -->|No| UPDATE_ONLY[Update line count<br>in state]
    UPDATE_ONLY --> LOOP

    CONTENT -->|Yes| INCREMENTAL{prev_count > 0?}
    INCREMENTAL -->|Yes| INC_EVENT[Emit incremental event<br>ts_start = new portion start<br>duration = new portion only]
    INCREMENTAL -->|No| FULL_EVENT[Emit full event<br>ts_start = session start<br>duration = full session]

    INC_EVENT --> WRITE[Append to<br>events-YYYY-MM-DD.jsonl]
    FULL_EVENT --> WRITE

    WRITE --> MARK[mark_session_processed<br>line_count = total_lines]
    MARK --> LOOP

    LOOP -->|Done| END([Ingestion complete])

    style START fill:#2d6a4f,stroke:#1b4332,color:#fff
    style END fill:#2d6a4f,stroke:#1b4332,color:#fff
    style INC_EVENT fill:#e76f51,stroke:#f4a261,color:#fff
    style FULL_EVENT fill:#264653,stroke:#2a9d8f,color:#fff
